game.name: Princess Gymnastic Olympics
game.description:
The Rio Olympics competition is just over and three of your favorite Disney princesses are known to be the best performers this year. Hey ladies! Do not take them easily since all of them got the success in securing the Olympic gold at one artistic event. Being the golden participants of the Olympiad, these girls are today invited to attend a popular fun photo session. For this purpose, they need to be dressed up perfectly. Join Princess Gymnastic Olympics game and be prepared to give your fashion advice to Ariel, Elsa, Mulan and Snow White!
All the lovely collection of gymnastics outfits and dancewear will be shown on the right side of the screen. Click the character and get ready to pick up the right outfit for each girl followed by the matching props and a suitable make-up! The wider range of costumes covered in glitter and playful prints will make it easier to find out a perfect dress for each girl. Complete their look with a colorful bouquet of flower and suitable medals in this HTML5 dressing game!
After finalizing a shimmering leotard for each of the beautiful princesses, you will have to help them to decide what type of rhythmic gymnastics routine they can carry out. Remember it is the first photo-shoot of their life so try to mix and match as many outfits as you can until you create the fabulous result. In case if you like this game, feel free to go through our extensive collection of free dress-up games for girls and get you surrounded by some extra fun environment.
